      "duration": 2.27,
      "size": 36288,
      "text": "两千多年前，毕达哥拉斯发现了一个关于直角三角形的秘密。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagoras-tree",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagoras-tree/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.41,
      "size": 38592,
      "text": "两条直角边上正方形的面积之和，正好等于斜边上正方形的面积。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagoras-tree",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagoras-tree/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.59,
      "size": 25488,
      "text": "如果让这条规则不停地长下去，会画出什么呢？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagoras-tree",
      "section_id": "build",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "build-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagoras-tree/xiaoxiao/build-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.44,
      "size": 23040,
      "text": "先画一个正方形，作为整棵树的树干。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagoras-tree",
      "section_id": "build",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "build-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagoras-tree/xiaoxiao/build-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.44,
      "size": 23040,
      "text": "在它的顶边上，架起一个直角三角形。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagoras-tree",
      "section_id": "build",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "build-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagoras-tree/xiaoxiao/build-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.93,
      "size": 30816,
      "text": "三角形的两条直角边，又各自成为一个新正方形的底边。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagoras-tree",
      "section_id": "grow",
      "line_id": "grow-1",
      "filename": "grow-grow-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagoras-tree/xiaoxiao/grow-grow-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.62,
      "size": 41904,
      "text": "对每个新正方形，重复同样的动作：架三角形，长出两个更小的正方形。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagoras-tree",
      "section_id": "grow",
      "line_id": "grow-2",
      "filename": "grow-grow-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagoras-tree/xiaoxiao/grow-grow-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.51,
      "size": 24192,
      "text": "每往上一层，正方形的数量就翻一倍。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagoras-tree",
      "section_id": "grow",
      "line_id": "grow-3",
