      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagoras-tree/xiaoxiao/grow-grow-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.15,
      "size": 34416,
      "text": "一分二，二分四，越长越密，渐渐撑开一片茂密的树冠。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagoras-tree",
      "section_id": "fractal",
